prompt_text: Describe your stay at a friend or relative’s house.
content_text: The last day that I had a with my friend or was at an up sells, it was basically a office party we all gathered in unabsorbed. We ordered her food from Zomato. Also we danced all night. There were some people who were drinking but non alcoholic so I enjoyed. And. Yes, we enjoyed a lot. We also watched a movie. We all gathered and watched the cricket match as well. So it was a lovely day and it was pleasant to be gathered around with my friends.
